    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/1a5674e2e002bc4c510ebe74831891fa.webp?t=1764323265\" width=598 height=45 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/69006ce763d3c170b76c8007550e4058.poster.avif?t=1764323265\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/69006ce763d3c170b76c8007550e4058.webm?t=1764323265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/69006ce763d3c170b76c8007550e4058.mp4?t=1764323265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Miami Horizon 2077</strong> is a 2D arcade game inspired by the GTA franchise cop chase experience. Enter a futuristic world setting in 2077 as a young street hustler attempting to make a name for himself in the criminal underworld by trying to pull off a series of dangerous street robbery where the likelihood of escape is almost impossible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Each run will start with a huge amount of money that you have just stolen from the heist. Your job is to avoid law enforcement and secure the money after a period of time. If you survive, you will be able to keep that money to buy upgrades and cars for your next heist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade based gameplay</strong> with high replayability value</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collects cash and armory</strong> on the way to your freedom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many different cars</strong> for you to collect and style on the street </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Changing the radio music</strong> to fit your taste while fighting your way out </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss Fight mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric retro vibe</strong> that will make you feel like a 80s hero</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/1c59aee612dd0fc90b13912686e6eaba.poster.avif?t=1764323265\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/1c59aee612dd0fc90b13912686e6eaba.webm?t=1764323265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305740/extras/1c59aee612dd0fc90b13912686e6eaba.mp4?t=1764323265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
